Package: measlesCFR
Title: Measles Case Fatality Rate
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alyssa", "Sbarra", , "asbarra@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    person("Allison", "Portnoy", , "aportnoy@mail.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A system for estimating measles case fatality ratios (CFRs) at the country, year, and age level for low- and middle-income countries. Users can inform covariate predictors in both/either the historic or future time periods, and the package will provide the resulting measles CFR estimates.
Imports:
    data.table,
    tidyverse,
    arm,
    msm,
    reticulate,
    stats,
    ggplot2,
